text: Dialytellus is a genus of aphodiine dung beetles in the family Scarabaeidae. There are at least three described species in Dialytellus. ==Species== * Dialytellus dialytoides (Fall, 1907) * Dialytellus humeralis (LeConte, 1878) * Dialytellus tragicus (Schmidt, 1916) ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * Category:Scarabaeidae
title: Dialytellus
